title: Places Mentioned in the Bible, World
name: Places Mentioned in the Bible, World
description: This dataset contains information on numerous places mentioned in the Bible. Along with the placemarks, there is historical information and biblical passages relevant to the locations. Sources include various Gazetteers, descriptions from the International Standard Bible Encyclopedia and Easton's Bible Dictionary. Data was found online at the Google Earth Community site, http://bbs.keyhole.com/ubb/showflat.php/Cat/0/Number/515491/an/0/page/6#515491
